Subject: Fifth Annual VW Buses n Boats Bash near Cincinnati Ohio

Hey Y'all,
Just taking a Friday privilege here to pimp the
upcoming Bus campout sponsored by the Ohio Valley
Tribe of the Full Moon Bus Club, so here goes:
Mark your calendars for the Fifth Annual VW Buses 'n
Boats Bash May 20-22 in Morrow, Ohio (32 miles north
of Cincinnati).  The event will feature Bus Camping,
canoeing, music, kids activities, technical demos,
World Famous Full Moon Breakfast Burritos, Pot luck
chili dinner, door prizes and MORE!!  Good people,
good food, and good fun! Here's the link to the event
web site:
http://www.geocities.com/buses_n_boats
Everyone is invited to enjoy some of that Good ole
Midwestern Bus Folks hospitality!!

Peace, John Baker
